function setup(){
  createCanvas(400, 400)
  textSize(50)
  img = loadImage("chimp.jpg")
}

function draw(){
  background("yellow")
  fill("red")
  rect(20, 20, 40, 40)
  fill("blue")
  
  for (i in items){
    w = random(width)
    h = random(height)
    text(items[i],w , h)
    image(img,w, h, 50, 70 )
    
    
  }
}
